		<paragraph indent="0" tabs="" style="normal" height="0" width="400" y="+6" x="12" type="text"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">This exercise will help you with ideas for the writing task. You'll have to choose which ideas you want to use as some won't support your opinion. When you have finished this exercise, you can decide whether you want to write a balanced 'for and against' composition or a 'one-sided' composition that gives your personal opinion and only discusses the arguments that support it.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
